---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import teacherPhoto from "../assets/teacher_faisal.png"; // replace with your actual file
---

<section class="py-12 bg-white text-center" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
    <h2
      id="about-heading"
      class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-10 text-gray-900"
    >
      About Us
    </h2>

    <!-- Teacher Profile -->
    <div
      class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm mb-12"
    >
      <div class="w-40 h-40 flex-shrink-0">
        <Image
          src={teacherPhoto}
          alt="Portrait of Quran teacher Hafiz Faisal Ahmed"
          width={300}
          height={300}
          class="rounded-full object-cover shadow-md"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="text-left">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Hafiz Faisal Ahmed</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2 leading-relaxed">
          A dedicated <strong
            >Quran teacher with over 3 years of experience</strong
          >, known for his gentle teaching style and deep command of Tajweed and
          Quran recitation. Faisal Ahmed has helped hundreds of students begin
          their Quranic journey with clarity, confidence, and love for the Book
          of Allah.
        </p>

        <!-- Stats -->
        <ul class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-gray-900">
          <li class="bg-white p-3 rounded-lg shadow text-center">
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-600">30+</p>
            <p class="text-sm">Students Taught</p>
          </li>
          <li class="bg-white p-3 rounded-lg shadow text-center">
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-600">3+ yrs</p>
            <p class="text-sm">Teaching Experience</p>
          </li>
          <li class="bg-white p-3 rounded-lg shadow text-center">
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-600">95%</p>
            <p class="text-sm">Parent Satisfaction</p>
          </li>
          <li class="bg-white p-3 rounded-lg shadow text-center">
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-600">100%</p>
            <p class="text-sm">Tajweed Accuracy</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Body Text -->
    <div
      id="about-text"
      class="text-left leading-relaxed space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-900"
    >
      <p>
        Shahi Online Quran Academy provides interactive online Quran classes for
        learners of all ages. Our mission is to make Quran learning simple,
        accessible, and enjoyable for every child—right from the comfort of your
        home.
      </p>

      <p>
        With over <strong>5 years of service</strong> in online Quran teaching, we
        have built a reputation for trust, quality, and personalized guidance.
      </p>

      <p lang="ar" class="text-2xl text-green-700 font-semibold">
        السلام عليكم ورحمة الله وبركاته
      </p>

      <p>Dear parents,</p>

      <p>
        Every child deserves a strong Islamic foundation. If you want your son
        or daughter to recite the Holy Quran with proper Tajweed and confidence,
        we offer a structured, child-friendly learning system that is proven to
        work.
      </p>

      <p>
        Our teaching method keeps children engaged and motivated, ensuring they
        learn with consistency, clarity, and discipline—without feeling
        overwhelmed.
      </p>

      <p>
        At Shahi Online Quran Academy, children learn Quran with Tajweed,
        <span lang="ar">القاعدة</span> (Qaida), handwriting practice, Makhraj training,
        and beautiful recitation—Insha’Allah.
      </p>

      <p>
        We offer both group and one-to-one sessions, allowing parents to choose
        what suits their child best. Every class is designed with patience,
        compassion, and focus on your child’s growth.
      </p>

      <p class="font-bold text-green-700">
        Give your child the gift of Quran today—an investment that lasts a
        lifetime.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
